OL,3,CEstate agent wants new law to force
OL,4,Csellers to survey homes before sale
OL,6,FAn estate agent in Guernsey is
OL,7,Flobbying the Government to force those
OL,8,Fselling their homes to get a full,
OL,9,Findependent survey done first.
OL,11,FNathan de Carteret from Cranfords
OL,12,Fargues that it will reduce pressure
OL,13,Ffor everyone involved in what is
OL,14,Falready a stressful process.
OL,16,FOne of the biggest issues is the time
OL,17,Fit takes for a bank in the island to
OL,18,Fapprove a mortgage - this has been put
OL,19,Fdown to stricter processes and a lack
OL,20,Fof resources.
