OL,3,CEstate agent wants new law to force
OL,4,Csellers to survey homes before sale
OL,6,FNathan says this is becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly common and could be
OL,8,Fsorted by requiring the seller to have
OL,9,Fa survey done before a house goes on
OL,10,Fthe market, rather than putting the
OL,11,Fburden on potentially multiple buyers.
OL,13,FHe explains: "It really doesn't help
OL,14,Fanyone doing so many surveys when it
OL,15,Fcould have been done right at the
OL,16,Fstart, before anyone even looks at the
OL,17,Fproperty to begin with."
