OL,4,Csellers to survey homes before sale
OL,6,FIn Scotland, it is already a legal
OL,7,Frequirement for sellers to provide a
OL,8,Fhome report and Nathan's pitch has
OL,9,Fcaught the attention of politicians
OL,10,Flocally.
OL,12,FThe new President of Guernsey's
OL,13,FHousing Committee, Deputy Steve
OL,14,FWilliams, says: "We're aware of this
OL,15,Fsuggestion and are informally reaching
OL,16,Fout to understand this further.
